bitNZ,is,a,Bitcoin,exchange,based,in,New,Zealand,The,exchange,allows,users,to,buy,and,sell,Bitcoins,for,New,Zealand,Dollars,NZD,Any,bid,or,ask,trades,must,be,matched,by,an,order,placed,by,another,user,and,will,remain,in,the,order,book,until,they,are,matched,or,canceled,The,bitNZ,API,enables,users,to,retrieve,their,own,private,data,as,well,as,the,exchange,s,public,data